T* (1. DATA AND ASSETS) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (- Polyvore disjoint split metadata and images for:) Tj
T* (- pair compatibility learning signal) Tj
T* (- type-prior computation) Tj
T* (- retrieval candidate pool and fallback references) Tj
T* (- DeepFashion Category and Attribute Prediction Benchmark for:) Tj
T* (- category classifier training \(`B2_trainCategory.py`\)) Tj
T* (- pattern classifier training \(`A3_TrainPatternClean.py`\)) Tj
T* (- Local model checkpoints for pair compatibility, pattern prediction, and category fallback are) Tj
T* (  exported from these training pipelines.) Tj
T* (- User wardrobe images persisted in MongoDB and runtime upload storage.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (DATASET USAGE CLARIFICATION) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. Polyvore \(compatibility dataset\):) Tj
T* (- Used in deployment-time pipeline for compatibility logic and retrieval.) Tj
T* (- Drives type prior table and candidate ranking pool.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2. DeepFashion \(supervised classifier training dataset\):) Tj
T* (- Used offline to train category and pattern models.) Tj
T* (- Trained weights and class mappings are then imported into the OutfitCompatibility runtime) Tj
T* (  \(`assets/models`\).) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2. PREPROCESSING PIPELINE) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. Accept uploaded image\(s\) through backend API.) Tj
T* (2. Auto-detect body visibility with YOLO pose and apply semantic crop hints.) Tj
T* (3. Generate foreground mask with selected remover \(U2Net/SegFormer/etc.\).) Tj
T* (4. Extract masked visual features \(color, brightness metrics\).) Tj
T* (5. Infer category via metadata match or fallback category model for external images.) Tj
T* (6. Infer pattern using pattern model or text heuristic fallback.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (3. SCORING STRATEGY) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Final score is computed as weighted fusion:) Tj
T* (`final = w_m*M + w_t*T + w_c*C + w_b*B + w_p*P`) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Current default weights:) Tj
T* (- model: 0.60) Tj
T* (- type_prior: 0.15) Tj
T* (- color: 0.12) Tj
T* (- brightness: 0.08) Tj
T* (- pattern: 0.05) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Five-band labels:) Tj
T* (- Excellent Match) Tj
T* (- Good Match) Tj
T* (- Borderline Acceptable) Tj
T* (- Weak Match) Tj
T* (- Mismatch) Tj
ET
endstream
