T* (CONCLUSION) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (This project demonstrates a practical computer vision compatibility system that is both) Tj
T* (technically grounded and application-ready. The implementation integrates model-based) Tj
T* (compatibility learning, visual-rule fusion, and full-stack deployment concerns such as API) Tj
T* (timing, response sanitization, and user-facing interpretability. The hybrid recommendation) Tj
T* (design is a strong practical contribution because it prioritizes user-owned wardrobe items) Tj
T* (while preserving fallback coverage from a large reference dataset. Overall, the system is) Tj
T* (suitable as a final-year CV project with clear research value and deployment relevance.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (FURTHER EXTENSION) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. Quantitative evaluation suite:) Tj
T* (- Top-k retrieval metrics \(Recall@K, MRR\) on controlled validation sets.) Tj
T* (- Calibration analysis for score-to-label alignment.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2. Latency optimization:) Tj
T* (- Smaller/faster local LLM variants and token-budget tuning.) Tj
T* (- Parallelized preprocessing and smarter cache invalidation.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (3. Better robustness for real-world uploads:) Tj
T* (- Improved category confidence handling and uncertainty propagation.) Tj
T* (- Enhanced crop validation for occlusion-heavy or multi-person photos.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (4. Personalization:) Tj
T* (- Learn user-specific style preferences from feedback history.) Tj
T* (- Reweight score components per user behavior over time.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (5. Production hardening:) Tj
T* (- Dedicated observability dashboards for pipeline stages and timeout rates.) Tj
T* (- Optional degraded operation mode for ML endpoints during DB outages.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (REFERENCES) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. Han, X. et al., "Learning Fashion Compatibility with Bidirectional LSTMs," ACM MM, 2017.) Tj
T* (2. Vasileva, M. et al., "Learning Type-Aware Embeddings for Fashion Compatibility," ECCV) Tj
T* (   Workshops, 2018.) Tj
T* (3. Polyvore Outfits Dataset \(disjoint splits and compatibility tasks\), public benchmark) Tj
T* (   resources.) Tj
T* (4. Ultralytics YOLOv8 Documentation \(pose estimation and keypoint inference\).) Tj
T* (5. Ronneberger, O. et al., "U-Net: Convolutional Networks for Biomedical Image Segmentation,") Tj
T* (   MICCAI, 2015.) Tj
T* (6. PyTorch Documentation, Meta AI.) Tj
T* (7. OpenCV Documentation.) Tj
T* (8. Ollama Documentation \(local LLM serving\).) Tj
ET
